thread.title: Graeme Jameson
thread.title_full: Ink Station reviewed by Graeme Jameson

author: Graeme Jameson
title: Graeme Jameson
text:
I have used other suppliers of non original laser products but quite simply Inkstation are the standout.
Their product lasts infinitely longer and produces high quality. I have used 2 other suppliers (one a very high profile brand) and their products were simply of very poor standard. I highly recommend Inkstation for the quality of their product and the very fast service. And for good measure, they were also cheaper.
